    "Including explanations alongside recommendations could shed some light on the actual scenario.",
    "Given current media practices, it is understandable that users have many misconceptions and confused opinions regarding how social media collect and process their data.",
    "These misconceptions make users feel insecure.",
    "Reasoning with the system for changing decisions, along with the explanation While investigating social media recommendation-related explanations, one intriguing discovery is that users often want to reason or converse with the system.",
